translation.Name: Rio Note - Museum #1
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_0: For the love of God! Those kids again! I've already banned them from here, but somehow they still manage to get inside! Just look at some of our cameras, all busted! And guess who's gonna pay for that? Me!
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_1: Of course, those kids ran away and I have to pay for all the damage. Luckily I've found some men that offered themselves to fix the cameras.
